    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-taken care of over the years\u2014perfect for someone looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road. Everything runs smoothly, and it\u2019s ready to hit the pavement with a new owner today. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
