    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and presents beautifully. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish, showing only the minor, superficial character marks consistent with careful ownership. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the upholstery is clean and well-preserved, and all interior electronics\u2014including the navigation and premium audio system\u2014operate flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, benefiting from a documented history of regular oil changes and preventative maintenance. It handles with precision, the transmission shifts smoothly, and the engine runs quietly. This is a reliable, well-sorted example that offers a premium driving experience for its next owner.",
