    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for checking out my car! It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape. It\u2019s super clean, runs beautifully, and is ready to hit the road with a new owner today. I\u2019ve truly loved driving this one, and I know you will too! Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look or have any questions at all\u2014I'm super happy to chat and help you out!",
      "price": 29500.0,
