    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3, a purist's specification featuring the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies. This unit delivers a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline, paired with a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis integrity. The factory limited-slip differential provides excellent lock-up, and the suspension geometry remains tight for precise turn-in. While it displays the honest patina of a driver's car, the drivetrain is robust and the cooling system has been refreshed to handle spirited canyon runs.",
